==English==

===Noun===
'''[[penny]] [[pincher]]'''
#{{idiom}} One who [[spends]] little [[money]]; one who is very [[frugal]] or [[cautious]] with money.  
#:''Over the years, he developed a reputation as a '''penny pincher''' who wouldn't spend money for anything.''

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[penninvenyttäjä]]

===Usage note===
*This term has a mildly negative connotation.

